@node SectionB.2 " Color Editor Resources: "

The xv color editor resources take the general form:

xv . state . item : val

where state is: ' default ', ' preset1 ', ' preset2 ', ' preset3 ', or '
preset4 ' and item is: ' huemap1 ' ' huemap2 ', ' huemap3 ', ' huemap4 ', '
huemap5 ', ' huemap6 ', ' whtmap ', ' satval ', ' igraf ', ' rgraf ', '
ggraf ', or ' bgraf '

@endnode

